		<td width="150" align="left" valign="top" class="row2"><span class="name"><a name="42202"></a><b>Mystikefini Ali</b></span><br /><span class="postdetails"><br /><br /><br />Joined: 06 Jan 2003<br />Posts: 17<br />Location: Vedbaek, Denmark; Portland, Oregon; Morehouse College, Atlanta, Georgia</span><br /></td>
		<td class="row2" width="100%" height="28" valign="top"><table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
			<tr>
				<td width="100%"><a href="viewtopic.php?p=42202&amp;sid=a9493115f741ebffd1b32aad33e5879a#42202"><img src="templates/subSilver/images/icon_minipost.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" border="0" /></a><span class="postdetails">Posted: Mon Feb 02, 2004 4:26 AM<span class="gen">&nbsp;</span>&nbsp; &nbsp;Post subject: Efinia, part 2</span></td>
				<td valign="top" nowrap="nowrap"><a href="posting.php?mode=quote&amp;p=42202&amp;sid=a9493115f741ebffd1b32aad33e5879a"><img src="templates/subSilver/images/lang_english/icon_quote.gif" alt="Reply with quote" title="Reply with quote" border="0" /></a>   </td>
